            <abstract>
                <p>
                    This is the hagiographical dossier on ʾAbbā Yoḥanni of Dabra ʿAśā, comprising <ref type="work" corresp="LIT7152GadlaYo">the long version of the Life</ref>, 
                    a <ref type="work" corresp="LIT7153MiraclesY">cycle of miracles</ref>, two hymns in honour of the saint
                    (<ref type="work" corresp="LIT7154MalkeaYo"/> and <ref type="work" corresp="LIT7155MalkeaYo"/>), and the 
                    <ref type="work" corresp="LIT4051Homily">homily by ʾAbbā Minās, bishop of Aksum, in honour of the saint</ref>.
                    The dossier is attested in MSS Ethio-SPaRe ADMY-003 and ADMY-014 <!-- ms records missing --> 
                   </p>
